1/2 (16 ounce) bottle reduced-fat raspberry vinaigrette salad dressing (such as KraftÂ® Raspberry Vinaigrette Lite)
n: Strawberry Spinach Salad With Feta and Bacon
des: "Strawberry spinach salad has feta cheese, sweet onion, and crumbled bacon all tossed with a raspberry vinaigrette dressing."
ins: Place spinach into a large salad bowl and slice strawberries over spinach; sprinkle with feta cheese, onion, and bacon bits. Pour raspberry dressing over salad and toss to coat.
